title: Recap of National Championship, Roster Breakdowns of Remaining Playoff Teams
itunes:title: Recap of National Championship, Roster Breakdowns of Remaining Playoff Teams
description:
DJ and Bucky are back with a new episode. To start off the show, the guys recap the College Football Playoff National Championship game between Clemson and LSU, while giving their evaluations on LSU QB Joe Burrow and more players from the game (1:45). After that, the pair look at the rosters of each of the remaining playoff teams in order to figure out which teams have enough players for a championship foundation (39:56).
